product information:
The Syncmaster 930B offers the option of using either a digital or analog interface for viewing images and text. The 1280x1024 pixel resolution provided by this Samsung LCD monitor ensures vivid and bright images on the screen. This 19-inch monitor delivers 8ms response time that lets you watch fast paced action-packed movies and videos without any visual noise. The contrast ratio of 700:1 and 300 cdm2 brightness generated by the Syncmaster 930B shows you images that are sharp, clear and absolutely beautiful. The inclusion of MagicTune and MagicBright features in this Samsung LCD monitor enhances the picture quality to let you view life-like images. The LCD technology of this 19-inch monitor makes it less than 8 inches deep, letting you save a lot of desk space.
